30002881@@@@@@During peak periods such as lunch time (12pm – 1.30pm) and dinner time (6pm – 7.30pm), it can get extremely crowded at popular eating spots such as Canteen A at the North Spine and Koufu at the South Spine.@@@@1@39@ntucle-docid:100; ntucle-sid:615@LMC@2019-06-14
