30002962@@@@@@In 2014, the e-commerce market was valued at roughly S$2.1trillion (Tanwami M., 2015), while in Singapore it was S$3.5billion (Jackie Y., 2014).@@@@1@22@ntucle-docid:106; ntucle-sid:593@LMC@2019-06-14
30002963@@@@@@When still in the early days, online shopping was often accompanied by (often justified) suspicion and paranoia with regards to false sites, information phishing and the questionable reliability of shipping and tracking (C. Lu, 2014).@@@@1@35@ntucle-docid:106; ntucle-sid:594@LMC@2019-06-14
30002964@@@@@@However, given the advent of secure online payment sites such as PayPal and AliPay (Terence L., 2012), e-commerce have since become a viable option for obtaining goods and commodities.@@@@1@29@ntucle-docid:106; ntucle-sid:595@LMC@2019-06-14
