30002966@@@@@@Given the prevalence of online shopping, keeping track of multiple impending shipments across a slew of shopping sites can be a hassle for the active online shopper.@@@@1@27@ntucle-docid:106; ntucle-sid:597@LMC@2019-06-14
30002967@@@@@@PROBLEM@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:106; ntucle-sid:598@LMC@2019-06-14
30002968@@@@@@For tracked packages, online shops usually come with a tracking service to track the package serial at its current phase and location from the warehouse to the destination.@@@@1@28@ntucle-docid:106; ntucle-sid:599@LMC@2019-06-14
