30003120@@@@@@Road accidents have always been a major problem in our society.@@@@1@11@ntucle-docid:110; ntucle-sid:708@LMC@2019-06-14
30003121@@@@@@Based on statistic provided by the Traffic Police Department in 2014 [1], there were a total of 20 fatalities and 3794 injuries due to road accidents.@@@@1@26@ntucle-docid:110; ntucle-sid:709@LMC@2019-06-14
30003122@@@@@@Road accidents can occur due to drink-driving and distracted driving.@@@@1@10@ntucle-docid:110; ntucle-sid:710@LMC@2019-06-14
30003123@@@@@@Therefore, there is a need to find a solution to reduce road accident.@@@@1@13@ntucle-docid:110; ntucle-sid:711@LMC@2019-06-14
30003124@@@@@@2 Problem@@@@1@2@ntucle-docid:110; ntucle-sid:712@LMC@2019-06-14
30003125@@@@@@World Health Organization (WHO) found that there is a worldwide increase in the use of mobile phones while driving, leading to a growing concern for road safety [2].@@@@1@28@ntucle-docid:110; ntucle-sid:713@LMC@2019-06-14
30003126@@@@@@Similarly, drinking and driving increases the likelihood of road accidents.@@@@1@10@ntucle-docid:110; ntucle-sid:714@LMC@2019-06-14
30003127@@@@@@Road accident may occur from both factors due to impairment in driving such as longer braking time and also reaction to traffic signal as well as speeding.@@@@1@27@ntucle-docid:110; ntucle-sid:715@LMC@2019-06-14
30003128@@@@@@Therefore, there is a need to improve the braking system of the car to prevent a crash or lessen the severity of collision.@@@@1@23@ntucle-docid:110; ntucle-sid:716@LMC@2019-06-14
30003129@@@@@@3 Solution@@@@1@2@ntucle-docid:110; ntucle-sid:717@LMC@2019-06-14
30003130@@@@@@In countries like Australia and United States, cars manufacturers such as Toyota, Audi and BMW has technology likes Automatic Emergency Brake (AEB) [3] as an option on luxury cars and higher-end models.@@@@1@32@ntucle-docid:110; ntucle-sid:718@LMC@2019-06-14
30003131@@@@@@These systems use radar, laser or cameras to sense an impending collision and automatically apply the brakes [4].@@@@1@18@ntucle-docid:110; ntucle-sid:719@LMC@2019-06-14
30003132@@@@@@To further improve the technicality of AEB and reduce road accident, motion sensors will be integrated to the front and back of the car which connects to the engine and the brake.@@@@1@32@ntucle-docid:110; ntucle-sid:720@LMC@2019-06-14
30003133@@@@@@These motion sensors can detect cars at close proximity.@@@@1@9@ntucle-docid:110; ntucle-sid:721@LMC@2019-06-14
30003134@@@@@@When it detects that the car is close to touching the bumper of the car ahead base on the speed and the braking distance, even after AEB is activated, it will automatically cease the engine, engage the brakes and stop the car from moving.@@@@1@44@ntucle-docid:110; ntucle-sid:722@LMC@2019-06-14
30003135@@@@@@4 Benefits@@@@1@2@ntucle-docid:110; ntucle-sid:723@LMC@2019-06-14
30003136@@@@@@Improving the system through the addition of motion sensors will benefit drivers who are distracted from driving or had their judgement impaired while driving.@@@@1@24@ntucle-docid:110; ntucle-sid:724@LMC@2019-06-14
30003137@@@@@@Furthermore, road traffic injuries cause considerable economic losses to victims, their families, and to nations as a whole.@@@@1@18@ntucle-docid:110; ntucle-sid:725@LMC@2019-06-14
30003138@@@@@@These losses arise from the cost of treatment and reduced productivity for those killed or disabled by their injuries.@@@@1@19@ntucle-docid:110; ntucle-sid:726@LMC@2019-06-14
30003139@@@@@@5 Implementation@@@@1@2@ntucle-docid:110; ntucle-sid:727@LMC@2019-06-14
