30003244@@@@@@Air-nalyser – Haze PSI Monitor@@@@1@5@ntucle-docid:112; ntucle-sid:1153@LMC@2019-06-14
30003245@@@@@@Background@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:112; ntucle-sid:1154@LMC@2019-06-14
30003246@@@@@@Haze has become a yearly occurrence in Singapore due to the resultant smog from Indonesia’s forest fires.@@@@1@17@ntucle-docid:112; ntucle-sid:1155@LMC@2019-06-14
30003247@@@@@@National Environmental Agency (NEA) reported that the average Pollutant Standards Index (PSI) level in 2015 is 3 times higher than in 2014.@@@@1@22@ntucle-docid:112; ntucle-sid:1156@LMC@2019-06-14
30003248@@@@@@Fine particulate matter PM2.5 is the main pollutant that contributes to the haze-filled air making it murkier and more acrid-smelling than the PSI number suggests.@@@@1@25@ntucle-docid:112; ntucle-sid:1157@LMC@2019-06-14
30003249@@@@@@Despite the frequent PSI spikes and dangers of haze, the air quality information is inconvenient to access and limited to government websites.@@@@1@22@ntucle-docid:112; ntucle-sid:1158@LMC@2019-06-14
30003250@@@@@@Problem@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:112; ntucle-sid:1159@LMC@2019-06-14
30003251@@@@@@Staying outdoors is hazardous as prolonged haze exposure leads to nasal inflammation.@@@@1@12@ntucle-docid:112; ntucle-sid:1160@LMC@2019-06-14
30003252@@@@@@The Straits Times reported a 20% increase in respiratory cases that were escalated by the haze in 2010.@@@@1@18@ntucle-docid:112; ntucle-sid:1161@LMC@2019-06-14
30003253@@@@@@Moreover, many do not take the precautionary measures of having their N95 masks or asthma inhalers on hand as they are unaware of the real-time PSI level.@@@@1@27@ntucle-docid:112; ntucle-sid:1162@LMC@2019-06-14
30003254@@@@@@The PSI information is currently limited to hourly and regional measurements.@@@@1@11@ntucle-docid:112; ntucle-sid:1163@LMC@2019-06-14
30003255@@@@@@Thus, Singaporeans may face health consequences if they do not take precautionary measures in time.@@@@1@15@ntucle-docid:112; ntucle-sid:1164@LMC@2019-06-14
30003256@@@@@@Solution@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:112; ntucle-sid:1165@LMC@2019-06-14
30003257@@@@@@Air-nalyser is a portable sensor-based instrument measuring 75.6mm x 50.3mm.@@@@1@10@ntucle-docid:112; ntucle-sid:1166@LMC@2019-06-14
30003258@@@@@@It measures the PSI level, visibility range and acrid-smell by taking samples of surrounding air and testing for quality subsequently.@@@@1@20@ntucle-docid:112; ntucle-sid:1167@LMC@2019-06-14
30003259@@@@@@It also has wireless capability for access to air quality information disseminated by the NEA.@@@@1@15@ntucle-docid:112; ntucle-sid:1168@LMC@2019-06-14
30003260@@@@@@In addition, it has an early warning system that urges users to reduce physical exertion, stay indoors and wear an N95 mask when the PSI level exceeds healthy limit (<100).@@@@1@30@ntucle-docid:112; ntucle-sid:1169@LMC@2019-06-14
30003261@@@@@@It can store up to three 3M-patented, foldable N95 masks and an asthma inhaler.@@@@1@14@ntucle-docid:112; ntucle-sid:1170@LMC@2019-06-14
30003262@@@@@@Benefits@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:112; ntucle-sid:1171@LMC@2019-06-14
30003263@@@@@@Air-nalyser helps Singaporeans to be more mindful of the haze by broadcasting the real-time PSI level.@@@@1@16@ntucle-docid:112; ntucle-sid:1172@LMC@2019-06-14
30003264@@@@@@At the push of a button, users will be alerted of the surrounding air’s PSI level.@@@@1@16@ntucle-docid:112; ntucle-sid:1173@LMC@2019-06-14
30003265@@@@@@Upon detection of air quality deterioration, users can respond immediately.@@@@1@10@ntucle-docid:112; ntucle-sid:1174@LMC@2019-06-14
30003266@@@@@@It is an all-in-one gadget that not only helps users to monitor real-time PSI levels but also prepares them with the necessary equipment in the event of haze.@@@@1@28@ntucle-docid:112; ntucle-sid:1175@LMC@2019-06-14
30003267@@@@@@The portability and convenience of Air-nalyser encourages users to take on a proactive role in protecting their health and well-being.@@@@1@20@ntucle-docid:112; ntucle-sid:1176@LMC@2019-06-14
30003268@@@@@@Implementation@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:112; ntucle-sid:1177@LMC@2019-06-14
30003269@@@@@@Our company will collaborate with NEA and 3M to manufacture Air-nalyser.@@@@1@11@ntucle-docid:112; ntucle-sid:1178@LMC@2019-06-14
