30003662@@@@@@Making laundry less of a chore – The Mobile Clothes Rack@@@@1@11@ntucle-docid:131; ntucle-sid:756@LMC@2019-06-14
30003663@@@@@@Background@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:131; ntucle-sid:757@LMC@2019-06-14
30003664@@@@@@Over 80% of Singapore’s population live in flats managed by the Housing Development Board (HDB).@@@@1@15@ntucle-docid:131; ntucle-sid:758@LMC@2019-06-14
30003665@@@@@@Of this 80% who live in HDB flats, the proportion of senior citizens age 65 years and above has been increasing, especially in older HDB estates such as Queenstown and Ang Mo Kio, where the proportion of senior citizens can be as high as 19% (Singapore Department of Statistics, 2014).@@@@1@50@ntucle-docid:131; ntucle-sid:759@LMC@2019-06-14
30003666@@@@@@However, majority of the older HDB estates are not well designed to suit the needs of the elderly as much of the building design was done decades ago when they were still in their prime.@@@@1@35@ntucle-docid:131; ntucle-sid:760@LMC@2019-06-14
30003667@@@@@@Problem@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:131; ntucle-sid:761@LMC@2019-06-14
30003668@@@@@@The current laundry design present in majority of older HDB flats requires users to lift poles loaded with their laundry into the bamboo pole holder or onto an external metal support with moderate precision.@@@@1@34@ntucle-docid:131; ntucle-sid:762@LMC@2019-06-14
30003669@@@@@@This would take some effort by the average middle aged adult and would definitely pose a problem to the elderly as they lack the strength they used to have.@@@@1@29@ntucle-docid:131; ntucle-sid:763@LMC@2019-06-14
30003670@@@@@@They might injure themselves in the process or even drop the fully-loaded pole from their flats, resulting in unfortunate passers-by to be injured.@@@@1@23@ntucle-docid:131; ntucle-sid:764@LMC@2019-06-14
30003671@@@@@@As Singapore’s population continues to lean towards an aging population, the proportion of senior citizens would only increase and hence this problem would affect more and more people, either directly or indirectly.@@@@1@32@ntucle-docid:131; ntucle-sid:765@LMC@2019-06-14
30003672@@@@@@Solution@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:131; ntucle-sid:766@LMC@2019-06-14
30003673@@@@@@To overcome this problem, a mobile clothes rack operated by a pulley-gearbox system could be installed in the households of the elderly such that they would be able to hang their laundry indoor with relative ease, piece by piece at shoulder level, before using the pulley system to gradually position their laundry out in the open.@@@@1@56@ntucle-docid:131; ntucle-sid:767@LMC@2019-06-14
30003674@@@@@@In the event of rainy weather, the pulley system can be used to position all the clothes indoor at one go instead of residents rushing to keep them, an additional convenience.@@@@1@31@ntucle-docid:131; ntucle-sid:768@LMC@2019-06-14
30003675@@@@@@Benefits@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:131; ntucle-sid:769@LMC@2019-06-14
30003676@@@@@@Besides benefiting the elderly, the mobile clothes rack could also help to improve the safety of children, as they might use a chair to compensate for their lack of height and risk falling out of the window.@@@@1@37@ntucle-docid:131; ntucle-sid:770@LMC@2019-06-14
30003677@@@@@@As the hanging of laundry would be done indoors, it creates a safer environment for children helping out in managing their household laundry.@@@@1@23@ntucle-docid:131; ntucle-sid:771@LMC@2019-06-14
30003678@@@@@@Implementation and Budget@@@@1@3@ntucle-docid:131; ntucle-sid:772@LMC@2019-06-14
30003679@@@@@@For the mobile clothes rack to be successfully implemented across Singapore, steps will be taken to collaborate with HDB and educate various HDB approved contractors such as Weiken.com Decor Pte Ltd (Housing Development Board, 24 September 2014) to carry out installation of the product.@@@@1@44@ntucle-docid:131; ntucle-sid:773@LMC@2019-06-14
30003680@@@@@@The mobile clothes rack would cost approximately $150, including installation fees.@@@@1@11@ntucle-docid:131; ntucle-sid:774@LMC@2019-06-14
30003681@@@@@@It would be made of lightweight stainless steel for its various components such as its gears, gear chains and hollow-core laundry poles and is expected to last at least 10 years.@@@@1@31@ntucle-docid:131; ntucle-sid:775@LMC@2019-06-14
30003682@@@@@@Conclusion@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:131; ntucle-sid:776@LMC@2019-06-14
30003683@@@@@@The pioneer generation has contributed much to Singapore and worked hard to transform it into a first world country.@@@@1@19@ntucle-docid:131; ntucle-sid:777@LMC@2019-06-14
30003684@@@@@@In order for them to enjoy their golden years and continue to contribute to the society, Singapore must develop a more elderly-friendly environment.@@@@1@23@ntucle-docid:131; ntucle-sid:778@LMC@2019-06-14
